title: F-18 Thundercat Falls Off of Aircraft Carrier USS Harry Truman
description:
On today's ZBT we've got 5 Rounds in the magazine... Round 1: A fella on TikTok made a frog army that turned into a case of good initiative, bad judgement. The result of his TikTok could be a mass extinction of up to 90 different types of frogs. Round 2: Military members are known to have many tattoos, sometimes they look great, sometimes they look like Chaps'. Either way, one service allows you to keep all of them. Round 3: Nearly 60,000 Guard and reserve troops are on the verge of being kicked out after refusing the COVID vaccine. Is that a good or bad thing considering the current problems in recruiting? Round 4: It seems like our NAVY should be advanced enough for an F-18 not to fall off an aircraft carrier because of some high wind. Round 5: A Brazilian model was forced into a wheelchair after politely holding in her gas for so long. Bonus Round: Will It Suck? Previewing Biden's next announcement. SUPPORT THE SHOW!!!
